## 🦈 Wireshark / tcpdump

| Command | What It Does |
|---------|-------------|
| `wireshark` | Open Wireshark GUI |
| `tcpdump -i eth0` | Capture traffic on eth0 |
| `tcpdump -i eth0 port 22` | Capture only SSH traffic |
| `tcpdump -i eth0 -w capture.pcap` | Save capture to file |
| `tcpdump -r capture.pcap` | Read saved capture file |

