## 🐚 Netcat (Network Swiss Army Knife)

| Command | What It Does |
|---------|-------------|
| `nc -lvp 4444` | Listen on port 4444 |
| `nc <IP> 4444` | Connect to a listener |
| `nc -u <IP> 514` | Send UDP packet |
| `echo "test" \| nc -u <IP> 514` | Send text via UDP |
| `nc -zv <IP> 1-100` | Port scan range 1-100 |

