## 📋 Log Analysis

| Command | What It Does |
|---------|-------------|
| `cat /var/log/auth.log` | View authentication logs |
| `tail -f /var/log/auth.log` | Watch logs in real time |
| `grep "Failed" /var/log/auth.log` | Search for failed logins |
| `grep "ssh" /var/log/auth.log` | Filter SSH events |
| `wc -l /var/log/auth.log` | Count log lines |
| `logger "test message"` | Manually generate a syslog entry |

