## 📦 Package Management

| Command | What It Does |
|---------|-------------|
| `apt update` | Refresh package list |
| `apt upgrade -y` | Install all updates |
| `apt install <package>` | Install a package |
| `apt remove <package>` | Remove a package |
| `apt search <term>` | Search for a package |

